h3cMulticastSnoop.name: h3cMulticastSnoop

revisions.description: The initial version of this MIB file.

h3cMulticastSnoop.contactinfo: Platform Team Hangzhou H3C Tech. Co., Ltd. Hai-Dian District Beijing P.R. China http://www.h3c.com Zip:100085

h3cMcsGlobalConfigTable.name: h3cMcsGlobalConfigTable
h3cMcsGlobalConfigTable.description: Table containing information about the global configuration of IGMP/MLD snooping.

h3cMcsGlobalConfigEntry.name: h3cMcsGlobalConfigEntry
h3cMcsGlobalConfigEntry.description: Entry containing information about the global configuration of IGMP/MLD snooping.

h3cMcsGlbSnoopingType.name: h3cMcsGlbSnoopingType
h3cMcsGlbSnoopingType.description: Type of the global configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

h3cMcsGlbRowStatus.name: h3cMcsGlbRowStatus
h3cMcsGlbRowStatus.description: The activation of a row enables IGMP/MLD snooping globally. The destruction of a row disables IGMP/MLD snooping globally.

h3cMcsGlbEntryLimit.name: h3cMcsGlbEntryLimit
h3cMcsGlbEntryLimit.description: Global maximum number of IGMP/MLD snooping forwarding entries.

h3cMcsGlbHostAgingTime.name: h3cMcsGlbHostAgingTime
h3cMcsGlbHostAgingTime.description: Global aging time of the multicast group on ports.

h3cMcsGlbRouterAgingTime.name: h3cMcsGlbRouterAgingTime
h3cMcsGlbRouterAgingTime.description: Global aging time of router ports.

h3cMcsGlbDropUnknownEnabled.name: h3cMcsGlbDropUnknownEnabled
h3cMcsGlbDropUnknownEnabled.description: Whether the feature of dropping unknown packets is enabled globally.

h3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigTable.name: h3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigTable
h3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigTable.description: Table containing configuration information about the specified VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigEntry.name: h3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigEntry
h3cMcsVirtualUnitConfigEntry.description: Entry containing information of the specified VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVUID.name: h3cMcsVUID
h3cMcsVUID.description: VLAN ID or VSI Index. Its value ranges from 1 to 4094 when type is VLAN, and from 0 to 0xFFFFFFFE when type is VSI

h3cMcsVUSnoopingType.name: h3cMcsVUSnoopingType
h3cMcsVUSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

h3cMcsVURowStatus.name: h3cMcsVURowStatus
h3cMcsVURowStatus.description: The activation of a row enables IGMP/MLD snooping in the VLAN or VSI. The destruction of a row disables IGMP/MLD snooping in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVUHostAgingTime.name: h3cMcsVUHostAgingTime
h3cMcsVUHostAgingTime.description: Aging time of the multicast group on ports in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVUMaxResponseTime.name: h3cMcsVUMaxResponseTime
h3cMcsVUMaxResponseTime.description: Maximum query response time in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVURouterAgingTime.name: h3cMcsVURouterAgingTime
h3cMcsVURouterAgingTime.description: Aging time of the router port in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVULastMemQryInterval.name: h3cMcsVULastMemQryInterval
h3cMcsVULastMemQryInterval.description: Last member query interval in the VLAN or VSI. A value of zero indicates that it is not configured in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVUDropUnknownEnabled.name: h3cMcsVUDropUnknownEnabled
h3cMcsVUDropUnknownEnabled.description: Whether the feature of dropping unknown packets is enabled in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVUPimSnoopingEnabled.name: h3cMcsVUPimSnoopingEnabled
h3cMcsVUPimSnoopingEnabled.description: Whether PIM snooping is enabled in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVUVersion.name: h3cMcsVUVersion
h3cMcsVUVersion.description: Version of IGMP/MLD snooping that is running on the VLAN. Value 2 represents IGMPv2 snooping and MLDv1 snooping, and value 3 represents IGMPv3 snooping and MLDv2 snooping.

h3cMcsVUQuerierEnabled.name: h3cMcsVUQuerierEnabled
h3cMcsVUQuerierEnabled.description: Whether the querier feature is enabled in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsVUGeneQuerierSourceAddress.name: h3cMcsVUGeneQuerierSourceAddress
h3cMcsVUGeneQuerierSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD general query packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

h3cMcsVUSpecQuerierSourceAddress.name: h3cMcsVUSpecQuerierSourceAddress
h3cMcsVUSpecQuerierSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD group-specific query packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

h3cMcsVULeaveSourceAddress.name: h3cMcsVULeaveSourceAddress
h3cMcsVULeaveSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD leave packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

h3cMcsVUReportSourceAddress.name: h3cMcsVUReportSourceAddress
h3cMcsVUReportSourceAddress.description: Source IP address of IGMP or MLD report packets. Its value is 255.255.255.255 or FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF:FFFF when not configured.

h3cMcsL2EntryTable.name: h3cMcsL2EntryTable
h3cMcsL2EntryTable.description: Table containing a list of Layer 2 multicast group entries.

h3cMcsL2EntryEntry.name: h3cMcsL2EntryEntry
h3cMcsL2EntryEntry.description: Entry of l2-multicast group, which is created for each group learned or configured in the VLAN or VSI.

h3cMcsL2EntryVUID.name: h3cMcsL2EntryVUID
h3cMcsL2EntryVUID.description: VLAN ID or VSI Index. Its value ranges from 1 to 4094 when type is VLAN, and from 0 to 0xFFFFFFFE when type is VSI.

h3cMcsL2EntryGroupAddress.name: h3cMcsL2EntryGroupAddress
h3cMcsL2EntryGroupAddress.description: IP address of the multicast group which the port joined.

h3cMcsL2EntrySourceAddress.name: h3cMcsL2EntrySourceAddress
h3cMcsL2EntrySourceAddress.description: IP address of the unicast source which the port joined.

h3cMcsL2EntryIfIndex.name: h3cMcsL2EntryIfIndex
h3cMcsL2EntryIfIndex.description: IfIndex value of the port that joined the Layer 2 IP multicast group entry.

h3cMcsL2EntryPortAttribute.name: h3cMcsL2EntryPortAttribute
h3cMcsL2EntryPortAttribute.description: Attribute of the port. 'd' means learned from IGMP/MLD packets, 's' means configured statically, 'p' means learned from PIM snooping, 'k' means obtained from the kernel, 'r' means learned from (*, *) entries, 'w' means learned from (*, G) entries.

h3cMcsPacketStatisticsTable.name: h3cMcsPacketStatisticsTable
h3cMcsPacketStatisticsTable.description: Table containing the IGMP/MLD packets statistics.

h3cMcsPacketStatisticsEntry.name: h3cMcsPacketStatisticsEntry
h3cMcsPacketStatisticsEntry.description: Entry containing the statistic information of IGMP/MLD packets that have been transmitted and received in the device.

h3cMcsStatisticsSnoopingType.name: h3cMcsStatisticsSnoopingType
h3cMcsStatisticsSnoopingType.description: Type of the snooping, IPv4 means the statistics for IGMP snooping, and IPv6 means the statistics for MLD snooping.

h3cMcsRxGeneryQueryNum.name: h3cMcsRxGeneryQueryNum
h3cMcsRxGeneryQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMP or MLD general query packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxV2SpecificQueryNum.name: h3cMcsRxV2SpecificQueryNum
h3cMcsRxV2SpecificQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv2 or MLDv1 group-specific query packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxV3SpecificQueryNum.name: h3cMcsRxV3SpecificQueryNum
h3cMcsRxV3SpecificQueryNum.description: The statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-specific query packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.name: h3cMcsRxV3SpecificSGQueryNum
h3cMcsRxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-and-source-specific query packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxV1ReportNum.name: h3cMcsRxV1ReportNum
h3cMcsRxV1ReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv1 report packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxV2ReportNum.name: h3cMcsRxV2ReportNum
h3cMcsRxV2ReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv2 or MLDv1 report packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxV3ReportNum.name: h3cMcsRxV3ReportNum
h3cMcsRxV3ReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 report packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxV3ErrCorReportNum.name: h3cMcsRxV3ErrCorReportNum
h3cMcsRxV3ErrCorReportNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 report packets with correct and incorrect records received on the device.

h3cMcsRxLeaveNum.name: h3cMcsRxLeaveNum
h3cMcsRxLeaveNum.description: Statistics of leave packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxPimHelloNum.name: h3cMcsRxPimHelloNum
h3cMcsRxPimHelloNum.description: Statistics of PIM hello packets received on the device.

h3cMcsRxErrorPacketNum.name: h3cMcsRxErrorPacketNum
h3cMcsRxErrorPacketNum.description: Statistics of error IGMP/MLD packets received on the device.

h3cMcsTxV2SpecificQueryNum.name: h3cMcsTxV2SpecificQueryNum
h3cMcsTxV2SpecificQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv2 or MLDv1 group-specific query packets sent from the device.

h3cMcsTxV3SpecificQueryNum.name: h3cMcsTxV3SpecificQueryNum
h3cMcsTxV3SpecificQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-specific query packets sent from the device.

h3cMcsTxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.name: h3cMcsTxV3SpecificSGQueryNum
h3cMcsTxV3SpecificSGQueryNum.description: Statistics of IGMPv3 or MLDv2 group-and-source-specific query packets sent from the device.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigTable.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigTable
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigTable.description: Table for configuring a port as a simulated member host for a multicast group.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigEntry.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigEntry
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupConfigEntry.description: Entry for configuring a port as a simulated member host for a multicast group.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupIfIndex.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupIfIndex
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupSnoopingType.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupSnoopingType
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupVlanID.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupVlanID
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupVlanID.description: Index uniquely identifying the specified VLAN in which a host on a port joined the multicast group.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupGroupAddress.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupGroupAddress
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupGroupAddress.description: IP address of the group to which the host belongs.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupSourceAddress.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupSourceAddress
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupSourceAddress.description: IP address of the source. A value of zero indicates that the multicast packets of this group can come from any sources.

h3cMcsPortJoinGroupStatus.name: h3cMcsPortJoinGroupStatus
h3cMcsPortJoinGroupStatus.description: This object is responsible for managing rows, which supports 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy'.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigTable.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigTable
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigTable.description: Table for configuring static group membership entries on a port.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigEntry.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigEntry
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupConfigEntry.description: Entry for configuring static group membership entries on a port.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupIfIndex.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupIfIndex
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupSnoopingType.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupSnoopingType
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupVlanID.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupVlanID
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupVlanID.description: Index uniquely identifying the specified VLAN in which a port statically joined the multicast group.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupGroupAddress.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupGroupAddress
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupGroupAddress.description: IP address of the multicast group.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupSourceAddress.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupSourceAddress
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupSourceAddress.description: IP address of the source. A value of zero indicates that the multicast packets of this group can come from any sources.

h3cMcsPortStaticGroupStatus.name: h3cMcsPortStaticGroupStatus
h3cMcsPortStaticGroupStatus.description: This object is responsible for managing the creation and deletion of rows, which supports 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy'.

h3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable.name: h3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable
h3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable.description: Table for configuring a port as a static router port.

h3cMcsRouterPortConfigEntry.name: h3cMcsRouterPortConfigEntry
h3cMcsRouterPortConfigEntry.description: Entry for configuring a port as a static router port.

h3cMcsRouterPortConfigIfIndex.name: h3cMcsRouterPortConfigIfIndex
h3cMcsRouterPortConfigIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

h3cMcsRouterPortConfigSnoopingType.name: h3cMcsRouterPortConfigSnoopingType
h3cMcsRouterPortConfigSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

h3cMcsRouterPortConfigVlanID.name: h3cMcsRouterPortConfigVlanID
h3cMcsRouterPortConfigVlanID.description: Index uniquely identifying the specified VLAN in which a port act as a static router port.

h3cMcsRouterPortConfigRowStatus.name: h3cMcsRouterPortConfigRowStatus
h3cMcsRouterPortConfigRowStatus.description: This object is a conceptual row entry that allows to add or delete entries to or from the h3cMcsRouterPortConfigTable. When an entry is created in this table 'createAndGo' method is used and the value of this object is set to 'active'. Deactivation of an 'active' entry is not allowed. When an entry is deleted in this table 'destroy' method is used.

h3cMcsPortConfigTable.name: h3cMcsPortConfigTable
h3cMcsPortConfigTable.description: Table for configuring the fast leave status, group limit number, group policy parameter and overflow replace status on a port in the specified VLAN.

h3cMcsPortConfigEntry.name: h3cMcsPortConfigEntry
h3cMcsPortConfigEntry.description: Entry containing information about the fast leave status, group limit number, group policy parameter and overflow replace status of a port in the specified VLAN.

h3cMcsPortConfigIfIndex.name: h3cMcsPortConfigIfIndex
h3cMcsPortConfigIfIndex.description: Port for which this entry contains information.

h3cMcsPortConfigSnoopingType.name: h3cMcsPortConfigSnoopingType
h3cMcsPortConfigSnoopingType.description: Type of the configuration. IPv4 means IGMP snooping configuration, and IPv6 means MLD snooping configuration.

h3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber.name: h3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber
h3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber.description: Group limit number of the port.

h3cMcsPortConfigFastLeaveStatus.name: h3cMcsPortConfigFastLeaveStatus
h3cMcsPortConfigFastLeaveStatus.description: Fast leave status of the port.

h3cMcsPortConfigGroupPolicyParameter.name: h3cMcsPortConfigGroupPolicyParameter
h3cMcsPortConfigGroupPolicyParameter.description: ACL number which is used as the group policy parameter of the port.

h3cMcsPortConfigOverflowReplace.name: h3cMcsPortConfigOverflowReplace
h3cMcsPortConfigOverflowReplace.description: This object is related to the object h3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber. If the current group number is less than the value of h3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber, any new group is permitted. If the current group number equals to the value of h3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber and the value of this object is enabled, the group with the minimum multicast address will be replaced by the new group. If the current group number equals to the value of h3cMcsPortConfigGroupLimitNumber and the value of this object is disabled, none of new group will be permitted.

h3cMcsPortConfigRowStatus.name: h3cMcsPortConfigRowStatus
h3cMcsPortConfigRowStatus.description: The object is responsible for managing the creation and deletion of rows, which supports 'active', 'createAndGo' and 'destroy'.
